fo        boɔ-ro    la   koɔraa
2s.NOM.WK love-IPFV FACT farmer
'you love a farmer'

# 4
# Strong form
# Adapted from a:114
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgement: g
Phenomena: pronouns
